  </div><!-- end #nav-col -->\t\t    \n    \t\t    \n        <div id=\"content-col\">\n            <div id=\"content\" role=\"main\">\n\n<div id=\"breadcrumb\" class=\"clearfix\" role=\"navigation\" aria-label=\"Breadcrumb Navigation\">\n<ul><li><a href=\"/\">Home</a><span class=\"crumbsep\">/</span></li><li><a href=\"/ucat/\">Undergraduate&nbsp;Catalog</a><span class=\"crumbsep\">/</span></li><li><a href=\"/ucat/colleges-depts/\">Colleges&nbsp;&amp;&nbsp;Departments</a><span class=\"crumbsep\">/</span></li><li><a href=\"/ucat/colleges-depts/urban-planning-public-affairs/\">College&nbsp;of&nbsp;Urban&nbsp;Planning&nbsp;and&nbsp;Public&nbsp;Affairs</a><span class=\"crumbsep\">/</span></li><li><a href=\"/ucat/colleges-depts/urban-planning-public-affairs/upp/\">Urban&nbsp;Planning&nbsp;and&nbsp;Policy</a><span class=\"crumbsep\">/</span></li><li><span class=\"active\">Minor in Sustainable Cities</span></li></ul>\n</div><!-- end #breadcrumb -->\n\n\t\t\t<h1 class=\"page-title\">Minor in Sustainable Cities</h1>\n\n\n\n<div id=\"textcontainer\" class=\"tab_content\" role=\"tabpanel\">\n\n<div class=\"sidebar\">\n\t<div id=\"sidebar-contact\">\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\t</div>\n</div>\n\n<h2>Requirements for the Minor</h2>\n<p>Students must complete 12 semester hours as outlined below. A GPA of 2.50/4.00 is required in courses taken towards the minor.</p>\n<table class=\"sc_courselist\" width=\"100%\">\n<caption class=\"hidden noscript\">Course List</caption>\n<colgroup>\n<col class=\"codecol\"/>\n<col class=\"titlecol\"/>\n<col align=\"char\" char=\".\" class=\"hourscol\"/>\n</colgroup>\n<thead>\n<tr class=\"hidden noscript\">\n<th scope=\"col\">Code</th>\n<th scope=\"col\">Title</th>\n<th scope=\"col\" class=\"hourscol\">Hours</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr class=\"even areaheader  firstrow\"><td colspan=\"2\"><span class=\"courselistcomment areaheader \">Required Courses</span></td><td class=\"hourscol\"></td></tr>\n<tr class=\"odd\"><td class=\"codecol\"><a href=\"/search/?P=US%20130\" title=\"US\u00a0130\" class=\"bubblelink code\" onclick=\"return showCourse(this, 'US 130');\">US\u00a0130</a></td><td>Principles of Urban Sustainability <sup>a</sup></td><td class=\"hourscol\">3</td></tr>\n<tr class=\"even\"><td class=\"codecol\"><a href=\"/search/?P=US%20230\" title=\"US\u00a0230\" class=\"bubblelink code\" onclick=\"return showCourse(this, 'US 230');\">US\u00a0230</a></td><td>Practices for Sustainable Cities <sup>b</sup></td><td class=\"hourscol\">3</td></tr>\n<tr class=\"odd\"><td colspan=\"2\"><span class=\"courselistcomment\">Select one of the following:</span></td><td class=\"hourscol\">3</td></tr>\n<tr class=\"even\"><td class=\"codecol\"><div style=\"margin-left:20px;\" class=\"blockindent\"><a href=\"/search/?P=COMM%20309\" title=\"COMM\u00a0309\" class=\"bubblelink code\" onclick=\"return showCourse(this, 'COMM 309');\">COMM\u00a0309</a></div></td><td>Environmental Communication</td><td class=\"hourscol\"></td></tr>\n<tr class=\"odd\"><td class=\"codecol\"><div style=\"margin-left:20px;\" class=\"blockindent\"><a href=\"/search/?P=ECON%20370\" title=\"ECON\u00a0370\" class=\"bubblelink code\" onclick=\"return showCourse(this, 'ECON 370');\">ECON\u00a0370</a></div></td><td>Environmental Economics</td><td class=\"hourscol\"></td></tr>\n<tr class=\"even\"><td class=\"codecol\"><div style=\"margin-left:20px;\" class=\"blockindent\"><a href=\"/search/?P=LALS%20269\" title=\"LALS\u00a0269\" class=\"bubblelink code\" onclick=\"return showCourse(this, 'LALS 269');\">LALS\u00a0269</a></div></td><td>Latin American Environmental Studies</td><td class=\"hourscol\"></td></tr>\n<tr class=\"odd\"><td class=\"codecol\"><div style=\"margin-left:20px;\" class=\"blockindent\"><a href=\"/search/?P=PPOL%20240\" title=\"PPOL\u00a0240\" class=\"bubblelink code\" onclick=\"return showCourse(this, 'PPOL 240');\">PPOL\u00a0240</a></div></td><td>Environmental Policy</td><td class=\"hourscol\"></td></tr>\n<tr class=\"even\"><td class=\"codecol\"><div style=\"margin-left:20px;\" class=\"blockindent\"><a href=\"/search/?P=PUBH%20320\" title=\"PUBH\u00a0320\" class=\"bubblelink code\" onclick=\"return showCourse(this, 'PUBH 320');\">PUBH\u00a0320</a></div></td><td>Ecologies of Health and Modern Life</td><td class=\"hourscol\"></td></tr>\n<tr class=\"odd\"><td class=\"codecol\"><div style=\"margin-left:20px;\" class=\"blockindent\"><a href=\"/search/?P=US%20202\" title=\"US\u00a0202\" class=\"bubblelink code\" onclick=\"return showCourse(this, 'US 202');\">US\u00a0202</a></div></td><td>Social Justice and the City</td><td class=\"hourscol\"></td></tr>\n<tr class=\"even\"><td class=\"codecol\"><div style=\"margin-left:20px;\" class=\"blockindent\"><a href=\"/search/?P=US%20390\" title=\"US\u00a0390\" class=\"bubblelink code\" onclick=\"return showCourse(this, 'US 390');\">US\u00a0390</a></div></td><td>Sustainability Internship</td><td class=\"hourscol\"></td></tr>\n<tr class=\"odd\"><td colspan=\"2\"><span class=\"courselistcomment\">Select one of the following:</span></td><td class=\"hourscol\">3</td></tr>\n<tr class=\"even\"><td class=\"codecol\"><div style=\"margin-left:20px;\" class=\"blockindent\"><a href=\"/search/?P=LAS%20493\" title=\"LAS\u00a0493\" class=\"bubblelink code\" onclick=\"return showCourse(this, 'LAS 493');\">LAS\u00a0493</a></div></td><td>Topics in Energy</td><td class=\"hourscol\"></td></tr>\n<tr class=\"odd\"><td class=\"codecol\"><div style=\"margin-left:20px;\" class=\"blockindent\"><a href=\"/search/?P=CME%20440\" title=\"CME\u00a0440\" class=\"bubblelink code\" onclick=\"return showCourse(this, 'CME 440');\">CME\u00a0440</a></div></td><td>Cities and Sustainable Infrastructure</td><td class=\"hourscol\"></td></tr>\n<tr class=\"even\"><td class=\"codecol\"><div style=\"margin-left:20px;\" class=\"blockindent\"><a href=\"/search/?P=PA%20494\" title=\"PA 494/ENGL\u00a0440/HIST\u00a0481\" class=\"bubblelink code\" onclick=\"return showCourse(this, 'PA 494');\">PA 494/ENGL\u00a0440/HIST\u00a0481</a></div></td><td>Special Topics in Public Administration <sup>c</sup></td><td class=\"hourscol\"></td></tr>\n<tr class=\"odd lastrow\"><td class=\"codecol\"><div style=\"margin-left:20px;\" class=\"blockindent\"><a href=\"/search/?P=UPP%20493\" title=\"UPP\u00a0493\" class=\"bubblelink code\" onclick=\"return showCourse(this, 'UPP 493');\">UPP\u00a0493</a></div></td><td>Topics in Urban Planning and Policy</td><td class=\"hourscol\"></td></tr>\n<tr class=\"listsum\"><td colspan=\"2\">Total Hours</td><td class=\"hourscol\">12</td></tr></tbody>\n</table>\n\n<table role=\"presentation\" border=\"0\" width=\"100%\" class=\"sc_footnotes\"><tr><td valign=\"top\" class=\"symcol\">a</td><td class=\"notecol\"><p><em><span class=\"sc_courseinline\"><a href=\"/search/?P=US%20130\" title=\"US\u00a0130\" class=\"bubblelink code\" onclick=\"return showCourse(this, 'US 130');\">US\u00a0130</a></span> is a requirement for the BA in Urban Studies. Urban Studies majors can pursue the minor, but they cannot apply <span class=\"sc_courseinline\"><a href=\"/search/?P=US%20130\" title=\"US\u00a0130\" class=\"bubblelink code\" onclick=\"return showCourse(this, 'US 130');\">US\u00a0130</a></span> to both the major and the minor. As a result, the course can be replaced with one of the 300-or 400-level courses in the selective lists above.</em></p></td></tr><tr><td valign=\"top\" class=\"symcol\">b</td><td class=\"notecol\"><p><em>Urban Studies majors who pursue the minor will take <span class=\"sc_courseinline\"><a href=\"/search/?P=US%20230\" title=\"US\u00a0230\" class=\"bubblelink code\" onclick=\"return showCourse(this, 'US 230');\">US\u00a0230</a></span> to fulfill the requirements of the minor, and the course cannot be used as a selective for the major.</em></p></td></tr><tr><td valign=\"top\" class=\"symcol\">c</td><td class=\"notecol\"><p><em>The special topics course that can be applied to the minor is Freshwater Lab.</em></p></td></tr></table></div><!--end #textcontainer -->\n\n\n